comments: DiVincenzo (NYK) reaches in and initiates contact to Sexton's (UTA) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.

Fontecchio's (UTA) left hand makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Brunson (NYK) during the drive. Sexton (UTA) and Brunson engage in incidental arm to arm contact after the ball is dislodged.
DiVincenzo (NYK) contests Sexton's (UTA) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Fontecchio (UTA) initiates contact with Randle's (NYK) arm, which affects Randle's ability to maintain control of the ball during his drive.
Sexton (UTA) establishes positive frontcourt position and then his left foot steps on the halfcourt line during his dribble. A Backcourt Violation should have been assessed.
Fontecchio (UTA) initiates contact with Brunson (NYK) that dislodges him after he gathers the loose ball.
Both Sexton (UTA) and Hart (NYK) meet at the same point while pursuing the loose ball and marginal contact occurs.
DiVincenzo (NYK) commits a take foul on Olynyk (UTA).
Horton-Tucker (UTA) legally contests DiVincenzo's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Quickley (NYK) makes clean contact with the ball and cleanly dislodges it away from Horton-Tucker (UTA) during the inbound play.
Markkanen (UTA) delivers contact to DiVincenzo (NYK) and dislodges him from his position as he gains possession of the loose ball.
Hart (NYK) commits a take foul on Markkanen (UTA).
Sexton (UTA) contests Brunson's (NYK) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
